title: The David Lynch Episode
description:
This year marks the 30th anniversary of David Lynch’s ‘Twin Peaks: Fire Walk With Me,’ and the 25th anniversary of ‘Lost Highway.’ To celebrate, Sean and Adam Nayman are diving deep into the unnerving, beautiful, often terrifying dream logic of their Lynchian fascinatination.

Host: Sean Fennessey
Guest: Adam Nayman
Producer: Bobby Wagner
